commentTextItems.html: turned to square leg and thats the end of the match, South Africa won by 118 runs

commentPostTextItems.html: This was more like a draw!, South Africa unable to bowl out Canada and they sedately proceeded to 136, they lost but the fact remains were not bowled out
Lots of catches went down and Maraj completed a chancy but resolute fifty
This has been a defensive match and must have provided lots of experience to Canada and some worries to South Africa in bowling and batting as they were not able to run off to a huge total
We would like to say goodbye to you know and look forward to providing more live coverage tomorrow

milestones.description: Ashish Bagai and Ishwar Maraj's 52-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 26 between Ian Billcliff and Fazil Sattaur
John Davison has become the top wicket-taker for CAN in ODIs with 7 wickets, going past Codrington's 6
Ashish Bagai has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (5) for CAN, going past Ian Billcliff
